{"tid":1854761,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過暴飲暴食+情緒問題？","createTime":"2020-01-31T16:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T00:03:44.000Z","uid":42927,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"77e98df865adf16017e6317f2fec8a80b2b31617","tid":1854761,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:12:26.000Z","msg":"我都唔知點解自己會暴飲暴食<br />\n可以將朱古力雪糕當三餐咁食<br />\n仲要日日都要食宵夜<br />\n淨係覺得自己因為好唔開心<br />\n而不停食嘢會令我開心一陣<br />\n我真係唔想咁樣但控制唔到<br />\n見到自己變到又重又肥<br />\n肥到完全唔想見人<br />\n真係好難受<br />\n但我又成日冇心情出街/做運動<br />\n最勁試過一個禮拜唔出街匿埋喺屋企淨係食瞓屙<br />\n<br />\n以前都已經試過一次暴飲暴食<br />\n但嗰陣自己下定決心減返肥<br />\n所以試過由80kg減到60kg<br />\n不過我依家我就由60kg食到變返80kg<br />\n我真係好憎我自己<br />\n有冇人明呀？"},{"pid":"8654cfdac76533b549c83d60c663e8cd26417c78","tid":1854761,"uid":52448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T17:19:14.000Z","msg":"食嘢好似係最方便令自己開心嘅一個方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果keep住唔開心，繼續落去都係keep住食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea05d7258af34d64827ae686b9f718b419e0c923","tid":1854761,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8654cfdac76533b549c83d60c663e8cd26417c78","tid":1854761,"uid":52448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T17:19:14.000Z","msg":"食嘢好似係最方便令自己開心嘅一個方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果keep住唔開心，繼續落去都係keep住食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T18:09:33.000Z","msg":"啱呀"},{"pid":"5812c5970df3454cbe343d99e6168d712f44032e","tid":1854761,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T18:25:13.000Z","msg":"王爾德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24559927eb9d402d62d5c0d9ab9854d2a652d29","tid":1854761,"uid":303311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T18:29:51.000Z","msg":"You are not alone<img src=\"/assets/faces